r: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; backface-visibility: hidden; display: inline-block; font-family: Icons; height: 1em; margin: 0px 0.25rem 0px 0px; opacity: 1; speak: none; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; width: 1.18em; font-size: 1em; left: -24px; position: absolute; top: 1px;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; line-height: 2; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;对TP自带的Auth类做了全面的抽象和重写，功能更细致，更完善，与系统彻底解耦（可以把类提出来，放到YII或者laravel里用都没问题），参考&amp;lt;code style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &amp;amp;quot;Andale Mono&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.3; margin: -0.2em 0.4em; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; white-space: pre; word-break: break-all;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;auth\\\\permission\\\\Auth;&amp;lt;/code&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/ul&amp;gt;&amp;lt;h2 style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; font-family: dashicons, &amp;amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei Mono&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei Mono&amp;amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.225; margin: 14px 0px; font-size: 1.3em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(82, 82, 82); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;a style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); margin-top: -10px; position: absolute;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;元素级权限控制机制&amp;lt;/h2&amp;gt;&amp;lt;ul class=\\&amp;quot;task-list list-paddingleft-2\\&amp;quot; style=\\&amp;quot;list-style-type: none;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;li class=\\&amp;quot;task-\\&amp;quot; style=\\&amp;quot;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span class=\\&amp;quot;icon square\\&amp;quot; style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; backface-visibility: hidden; display: inline-block; font-family: Icons; height: 1em; margin: 0px 0.25rem 0px 0px; opacity: 1; speak: none; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; width: 1.18em; font-size: 1em; left: -24px; position: absolute; top: 1px;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;可以对页面里的单个元素（一个按钮，表格里的一个字段等）做精细化控制，是否可见，是否可直接编辑。比如设置某表格，在A角色登陆时，当B字段的值为5的时候，C字段是否可编辑，删除按钮是否可用等，十分灵活，只需要编写配置文件即可 ，参考&amp;lt;code style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &amp;amp;quot;Andale Mono&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.3; margin: -0.2em 0.4em; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; white-space: pre; word-break: break-all;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;auth\\\\view\\\\Auth;&amp;lt;/code&amp;gt;&amp;amp;nbsp;配置文件参考&amp;lt;code style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &amp;amp;quot;Andale Mono&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.3; margin: -0.2em 0.4em; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; white-space: pre; word-break: break-all;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;app\\\\extra&amp;lt;/code&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/ul&amp;gt;&amp;lt;h2 style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; font-family: dashicons, &amp;amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei Mono&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei Mono&amp;amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.225; margin: 14px 0px; font-size: 1.3em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(82, 82, 82); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;a style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); margin-top: -10px; position: absolute;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;分片上传处理&amp;lt;/h2&amp;gt;&amp;lt;ul class=\\&amp;quot;task-list list-paddingleft-2\\&amp;quot; style=\\&amp;quot;list-style-type: none;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;li class=\\&amp;quot;task-\\&amp;quot; style=\\&amp;quot;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span class=\\&amp;quot;icon square\\&amp;quot; style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; backface-visibility: hidden; display: inline-block; font-family: Icons; height: 1em; margin: 0px 0.25rem 0px 0px; opacity: 1; speak: none; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; width: 1.18em; font-size: 1em; left: -24px; position: absolute; top: 1px;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;重写上传处理逻辑，TP官方自带的上传类使用方便，但因为不是分片上传（参考think\\\\File类里的move方法使用的move_uploaded_file函数），这意味着如果需要上传G级文件，将导致性能问题（几乎是不可能完成）。为此重写了上传处理逻辑，配合webuploader插件（百度官方插件），实现分片上传，上传G级文件也没问题，前后端组件都已经封装，只需调用一个函数即可,包括单/多文件上传，单/多图片上传，前端调用参考&amp;lt;code style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &amp;amp;quot;Andale Mono&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.3; margin: -0.2em 0.4em; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; white-space: pre; word-break: break-all;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;extend\\\\builder\\\\integrationTags&amp;lt;/code&amp;gt;的&amp;lt;code style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &amp;amp;quot;Andale Mono&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.3; margin: -0.2em 0.4em; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; white-space: pre; word-break: break-all;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;upload&amp;lt;/code&amp;gt;方法，分片处理逻辑参考&amp;amp;nbsp;&amp;lt;code style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &amp;amp;quot;Andale Mono&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.3; margin: -0.2em 0.4em; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; white-space: pre; word-break: break-all;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;extend\\\\upload\\\\uploader&amp;lt;/code&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/ul&amp;gt;&amp;lt;h2 style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; font-family: dashicons, &amp;amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei Mono&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei Mono&amp;amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.225; margin: 14px 0px; font-size: 1.3em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(82, 82, 82); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;a style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); margin-top: -10px; position: absolute;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;应用化&amp;lt;/h2&amp;gt;&amp;lt;ul class=\\&amp;quot;task-list list-paddingleft-2\\&amp;quot; style=\\&amp;quot;list-style-type: none;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;li class=\\&amp;quot;task-\\&amp;quot; style=\\&amp;quot;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span class=\\&amp;quot;icon square\\&amp;quot; style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; backface-visibility: hidden; display: inline-block; font-family: Icons; height: 1em; margin: 0px 0.25rem 0px 0px; opacity: 1; speak: none; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; width: 1.18em; font-size: 1em; left: -24px; position: absolute; top: 1px;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;平台本身只有后台管理，其他功能需要安装应用来实现，拥有十分完善的安装，卸载，应用打包，数据配置自动生成机制。基本可以理解为安卓系统和apk安装包之间的关系，平台安装后自带有一个博客系统供开发者参考学习 ，参考&amp;lt;code style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &amp;amp;quot;Andale Mono&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.3; margin: -0.2em 0.4em; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; white-space: pre; word-break: break-all;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;app\\\\admin\\\\logic\\\\Module;&amp;lt;/code&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/ul&amp;gt;&amp;lt;h2 style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; font-family: dashicons, &amp;amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei Mono&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei Mono&amp;amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.225; margin: 14px 0px; font-size: 1.3em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(82, 82, 82); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;a style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); margin-top: -10px; position: absolute;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;自定义依赖注入机制&amp;lt;/h2&amp;gt;&amp;lt;ul class=\\&amp;quot;task-list list-paddingleft-2\\&amp;quot; style=\\&amp;quot;list-style-type: none;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;li class=\\&amp;quot;task-\\&amp;quot; style=\\&amp;quot;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span class=\\&amp;quot;icon square\\&amp;quot; style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; backface-visibility: hidden; display: inline-block; font-family: Icons; height: 1em; margin: 0px 0.25rem 0px 0px; opacity: 1; speak: none; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; width: 1.18em; font-size: 1em; left: -24px; position: absolute; top: 1px;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;拥有一套自定义的依赖注入机制，trait引入，通过__get实现，可以在任何类里仅通过调用自身属性即可得到任何模块下的model、logic、service的实例，无需繁琐的使用model方法实例化模型，参考&amp;amp;nbsp;&amp;lt;code style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, &amp;amp;quot;Andale Mono&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.3; margin: -0.2em 0.4em; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; white-space: pre; word-break: break-all;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;app\\\\common\\\\common\\\\set;&amp;lt;/code&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/ul&amp;gt;&amp;lt;h2 style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; font-family: dashicons, &amp;amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei Mono&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;amp;quot;, &amp;amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei Mono&amp;amp;quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.225; margin: 14px 0px; font-size: 1.3em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(82, 82, 82); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;a style=\\&amp;quot;box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); margin-top: -10px; position: absolute;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;齐全的调用示例&amp;lt;/h2&amp;gt;&amp;lt;ul class=\\&amp;quot;task-list list-paddingleft-2\\&amp;quot; style=\\&amp;quot;list-style-type: none;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;li class=\\&amp;quot;task-\\&amp;quot; style=\\&amp;quot;\\&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span class=\\&amp;quot;i